  m_Name: ChinaMasculinityR1Graph
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp-Editor::DS.Data.Save.DSGraphSaveDataSO
  <FileName>k__BackingField: ChinaMasculinityR1
  <Groups>k__BackingField: []
  <DialogueNodes>k__BackingField:
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 82315d37-f628-4d6f-8616-90d4f90ee766
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName3
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 24e57c24-a0c0-49a1-9b90-8914e9525123
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 1748.8, y: 67.2}
    <Text>k__BackingField: 'Secondly, global capitalism and growing income also mean
      that more people in China can travel. In certain cases, being exposed to another
      country also deepens one''s fascination with the culture of that country.

'
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6584716134473236321, guid: 042a111696a864549ae6a2be7ac704b9, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: -2441277322969603615, guid: 5d833bbe5effc5245b8c8e5380102d6f, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 24e57c24-a0c0-49a1-9b90-8914e9525123
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName4
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 7398d7a1-bbd9-4750-a7e3-c4acef7e0ebd
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 2551.2, y: 67.2}
    <Text>k__BackingField: "In the context of South Korea, the case of \"Seoul syndrome\"
      has recently been noted amongst China's youth, where they suffer intense nostalgia
      and homesickness for South Korea, which has been noted to deepen China's youth
      fascination for South Korean culture, especially that country\u2019s culture."
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6584716134473236321, guid: 042a111696a864549ae6a2be7ac704b9, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: -2441277322969603615, guid: 5d833bbe5effc5245b8c8e5380102d6f, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 52b55f11-856a-434f-94a1-02ea6f61c8e6
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName2
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: Continue...
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 82315d37-f628-4d6f-8616-90d4f90ee766
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 977.6, y: 53.6}
    <Text>k__BackingField: K-pop male celebrities tend to look more effeminate and
      gentle. Hence, as Chinese women become richer and consume more of such media,
      their tastes and preferences for masculinity also shift towards such traits.
      In turn, this allows Chinese women to negotiate how contemporary masculinity
      in China is shaped through the consumption of such culture as more companies
      would try to appeal to this trend, therefore normalizing such masculinity.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6584716134473236321, guid: 042a111696a864549ae6a2be7ac704b9, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: -2441277322969603615, guid: 5d833bbe5effc5245b8c8e5380102d6f, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: e187fe49-79bf-4f97-94e6-db17f5dbfb76
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName10
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 8752.8, y: 90.4}
    <Text>k__BackingField: Consequently, the increase in consumption of beauty products
      amongst Chinese men is a way of challenging how masculinity is portrayed in
      China. Now, more men in China are starting to embrace the more contemporary
      form of masculinity, which has an emphasis on softness.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6584716134473236321, guid: 042a111696a864549ae6a2be7ac704b9, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: -2441277322969603615, guid: 5d833bbe5effc5245b8c8e5380102d6f, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 226f2f97-6cba-470b-aa92-04e4c996bcf1
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName9
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: e187fe49-79bf-4f97-94e6-db17f5dbfb76
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 8022.4, y: 79.2}
    <Text>k__BackingField: 'There are reports that men''s increasing focus on grooming
      is due to the influence of girlfriends and wives. There is a high likelihood
      of them being part of the consumer base that demands South Korean idol culture,
      given its popularity. '
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6584716134473236321, guid: 042a111696a864549ae6a2be7ac704b9, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: -2441277322969603615, guid: 5d833bbe5effc5245b8c8e5380102d6f, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: a75698be-2a23-4c6e-9f20-41eb6c7826a6
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName7
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 73754985-6f14-4de5-9d9f-75de203ef4ac
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 6500.8, y: 90.4}
    <Text>k__BackingField: 'According to research, the rise in income amongst Chinese
      men, for instance, has led to increased focus on grooming. In particular, Chinese
      men between the ages of 18 and 26 have become the main driving force of the
      male beauty market.

'
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6584716134473236321, guid: 042a111696a864549ae6a2be7ac704b9, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: -2441277322969603615, guid: 5d833bbe5effc5245b8c8e5380102d6f, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 5d7ac371-347b-4aba-b624-a0b5d01d1074
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName6
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: a75698be-2a23-4c6e-9f20-41eb6c7826a6
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 5764.8, y: 76.799995}
    <Text>k__BackingField: Lastly, growing income has also been noted to have a strong
      correlation with demand for beauty products in China.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6584716134473236321, guid: 042a111696a864549ae6a2be7ac704b9, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: -2441277322969603615, guid: 5d833bbe5effc5245b8c8e5380102d6f, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: de7b3002-5558-482a-b306-0fbd192081ec
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName5
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 5d7ac371-347b-4aba-b624-a0b5d01d1074
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 5049.6, y: 67.2}
    <Text>k__BackingField: Hence, in the context of China, rising income and being
      able to travel to South Korea also further spur the exportation of South Korean
      culture in China, which not only leads to higher demand for the soft and effeminate
      masculinity in China, but also a greater normalisation of such traits in men.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6584716134473236321, guid: 042a111696a864549ae6a2be7ac704b9, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: -2441277322969603615, guid: 5d833bbe5effc5245b8c8e5380102d6f, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 73754985-6f14-4de5-9d9f-75de203ef4ac
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName8
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 226f2f97-6cba-470b-aa92-04e4c996bcf1
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 7273.6, y: 117.6}
    <Text>k__BackingField: Other than growing income leading to more Chinese men
      focusing on grooming and hygiene, another factor that leads to this consequence
      and is also indirectly tied to capitalism is the popularity of South Korean
      idols imported into China by global capitalism.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6584716134473236321, guid: 042a111696a864549ae6a2be7ac704b9, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: -2441277322969603615, guid: 5d833bbe5effc5245b8c8e5380102d6f, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 7398d7a1-bbd9-4750-a7e3-c4acef7e0ebd
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName888
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: b2b41d30-f9f5-4557-ac18-c30cf4de2d6e
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 3615.2, y: 94.4}
    <Text>k__BackingField: After all, travelling is a luxury.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6584716134473236321, guid: 042a111696a864549ae6a2be7ac704b9, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: -2441277322969603615, guid: 5d833bbe5effc5245b8c8e5380102d6f, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: b2b41d30-f9f5-4557-ac18-c30cf4de2d6e
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName77
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: de7b3002-5558-482a-b306-0fbd192081ec
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 4332.8, y: 94.4}
    <Text>k__BackingField: Without the finances to travel, not many Chinese people
      may have the opportunity to experience the culture first hand which would not
      have made this fascination as deep as before, as most would probably be more
      focused on trying to keep up with the cost of living and may not necessarily
      be thinking about this sort of thing.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6584716134473236321, guid: 042a111696a864549ae6a2be7ac704b9, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: -2441277322969603615, guid: 5d833bbe5effc5245b8c8e5380102d6f, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: d4ce026e-1625-41ea-9e6c-7e4dc07edb22
    <Name>k__BackingField: DialogueName
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 238a2a8b-f52f-49d8-81c8-78aeee07512c
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: -388.8, y: 51.199997}
    <Text>k__BackingField: Firstly, as K-pop culture becomes more popular in China,
      women's demand for it also increases, especially as their purchasing power
      rises, which in turn leads to stronger exports of soft masculinity.
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6584716134473236321, guid: 042a111696a864549ae6a2be7ac704b9, type: 3}
    <RightSprites>k__BackingField: []
    <IsChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <IsRememberChoiceNode>k__BackingField: 0
    <RememberSO>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
    ChoiceSO:
    - {fileID: 0}
    BackgroundImage: {fileID: -2441277322969603615, guid: 5d833bbe5effc5245b8c8e5380102d6f, type: 3}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 238a2a8b-f52f-49d8-81c8-78aeee07512c
    <Name>k__BackingField: 11
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: New Choice
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 52b55f11-856a-434f-94a1-02ea6f61c8e6
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 300.8, y: 51.199997}
    <Text>k__BackingField: As a testament to how popular it is, about 56% of all
      women in China are fans of Kpop idol groups, That's more than half of the population!
    <Actions>k__BackingField: []
    <LeftSprites>k__BackingField:
    - {fileID: 6584716134473236321, guid: 042a111696a864549ae6a2be7ac704b9, type: 3}
